2.00	Novar_plc	Novar plc	Novar plc was an international group based in the United Kingdom with core activities in Security Systems, Aluminium Extrusion and Cheque Printing. It was bought by Honeywell in 2005, and its activities merged. Under its previous name, MB-Caradon plc, it was a constituent of the FTSE 100 Index.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/5/51/NovarPLC-logo.jpg/150px-NovarPLC-logo.jpg
